{"tid":1321079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咬斷手指事件有冇人講大話？","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T14:47:35.000Z","uid":67356,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"926cfe8c0a4e3ad3bd516999d44b15792994211c","tid":1321079,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"消息人士指出，被咬斷指的警員是姓梁新界南總區刑事部沙展，入職26年，昨日被借調至隔離區的機動部隊作清場行動，當時他已執勤近12小時。事發時新城市廣場發生衝突，有警員被示威者包圍及襲擊，梁遂進行拘捕，示威者作出掙扎及意圖逃脫，其間梁的右手無名指第一節整個被示威者咬斷。該人士又指<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">插眼事件是假的，「搵藉口去逃避」，直指反政府人士、支持示威者及暴徒的人全是歪理</span></strong>。<br />\n民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆稱，今早已與斷手指的受傷警長通過電話，了解他的情況。葛珮帆表示，該名警長提及，事發時見到有一名警官諸人圍毆，他欲上前協助時，於混亂中，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其中一名示威者捉住他的手指，然後便咬斷了他的手。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3fXV0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3fXV0p.jpg&h=53d67e78&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kR5UdM5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkR5UdM5.jpg&h=4012af17&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUAUdM5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUAUdM5.jpg&h=e2ef5872&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7HWr66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7HWr66.jpg&h=9f4c1f73&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n示威者用邊隻手捉住佢手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個假 邊個搵藉口 邊個全部歪理？"},{"pid":"26548e83d2a7d52347bbdaaa481b59e82ed6d099","tid":1321079,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"狗賊幾時有半句真話？"},{"pid":"d6d34a3b8eca0d4fc80afc7d86c4596441ba836b","tid":1321079,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"四張圖掉轉咗次序<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca7c1126f41b390e7aaa166f3ca9c5484922c83","tid":1321079,"uid":9